Name:           elytambiance
Version:        %%VERSION%%
Release:        1
Summary:        Native ambient sound generator built for the BSD desktop
License:        GPLv3
URL:            https://github.com/elytraVIII/ElytAmbience
BuildArch:      noarch
Requires:       python3, python3-gobject, gtk3, gstreamer1-plugins-good

%description
Native ambient sound generator built for the BSD desktop. Optimized for FreeBSD and GhostBSD.

%install
mkdir -p %{buildroot}
cp -a %%STAGING_DIR%%/* %{buildroot}/

%files
/usr/bin/elytambiance
/usr/share/elytambiance/
/usr/share/applications/elytambiance.desktop
/usr/share/icons/hicolor/scalable/apps/elytambiance.svg
/usr/share/glib-2.0/schemas/org.elytlabs.elytambiance.gschema.xml
/usr/lib/python*/*-packages/elytambiance/

%changelog
* Sat May 30 2026 elytraVIII <elytraVIII@gmail.com> - %%VERSION%%-1
- Release %%VERSION%%
